      • GetArchiveClass

        public static com.ser.blueline.metaDataComponents.IArchiveClass GetArchiveClass(com.ser.blueline.ISession session,
                                                                                java.lang.String className)
                                                                         throws java.lang.Exception
        Gets archive class from Doxis4 by class name or ID

        After class will be requested - it will be stored in ConcurrentMap and for the next time it was taken from that map

        Parameters:
        session - Doxis4 Session object
        className - Class name or ID
        Returns:
        Archive class object. Will return null if class will not be found
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - if there will be some errors with connection to Doxis4
        See Also:
        ISession, IArchiveClass
